It can be noticed that this definition of the FOMS only consider the largest possible energy output of TENG in the ideal situation, ignoring the universally existed breakdown effect, which will affect the energy output greatly, which cannot reflect the real merit of the TENG. In order to make FOM suitable for practical situations with the breakdown effect, the FOM of TENG should be revised based on Eem. Thus, the revised FOMS and FOMP can be redefined by:4FOMS=2ε0σ2EemAxmax\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
